videos.description: John Mooney makes Syracuse pay with a pair of inside buckets early in the first half.
videos.headline: Mooney flies in for putback dunk

videos.description: Marek Dolezaj times a block perfectly as Notre Dame looked to have an easy bucket.
videos.headline: Dolezaj pins block against glass

videos.description: Tyus Battle scores on consecutive possessions to give Syracuse its biggest lead of the game.
videos.headline: Back-to-back Battle buckets give Cuse the lead

videos.description: Notre Dame takes a halftime lead as Nate Laszewski buries a contested corner 3-pointer at the buzzer.
videos.headline: Laszewski buries buzzer-beater with man in his face

videos.description: Oshae Brissett penetrates for a big dunk to silence the Notre Dame crowd.
videos.headline: Brissett drives for thunderous dunk

videos.description: John Mooney dominates in the paint to finish a couple big buckets for Notre Dame in the second half.
videos.headline: Mooney muscles in pair of buckets to steal momentum
